# Dataset

This project uses the **Gunshot Audio Dataset** available on Kaggle.

Dataset Link:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/emrahaydemr/gunshot-audio-dataset

## Dataset Contents

The dataset contains recordings from multiple firearm categories including:

- AK-47
- IMI Desert Eagle
- AK-12
- M16
- M249
- MG-42
- MP5
- Zastava M92

These audio samples were used for feature extraction (MFCC), preprocessing, model training, and evaluation.

